; Source: Computer Science Logo Style, Volume 2 file/input examples.
; Source URL: https://people.eecs.berkeley.edu/~bh/v2ch1/files.html
; This deterministic input fixture exercises the same READWORD/READLIST/READCHAR
; shape without depending on an interactive terminal.
print readword
show readlist
print eofp
print readchar
print eofp
